{
    "post_id": 21822,
    "title": "אל רם חסין יה | El Ram Ḥasin Yah, a piyyut for Sukkot by Shlomo haPaytan (egal adaptation by Noam Sienna, 2012)",
    "author": "Noam Sienna",
    "coauthors": [
        {
            "name": "Noam Sienna",
            "bio": "Noam Sienna is a Hebrew calligrapher, scholar, and manuscript artist, with degrees in religion, anthropology, education, and history from Brandeis University, the University of Toronto, and currently in progress at the University of Minnesota. His work explores the relationship between text, image, colour, and light, inspired by the tradition of Jewish books throughout the centuries, and with a particular focus on Jewish communities of the Middle East and North Africa. He has taught about Hebrew calligraphy and Jewish manuscript illumination to groups and individuals of all ages in both academic and hands-on settings. His graduate work in Jewish History and Museum Studies provides his art with deep roots and a commitment to seeing the past come alive again in the process.",
            "website": "http://siennajewisharts.com",
            "avatar": "https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/NoamSienna_200sq-96x96.png",
            "profile_link": "https://opensiddur.org/profile/noam-sienna"
        },
        {
            "name": "Shlomo haPaytan",
            "bio": "Shlomo \"Ḥazaq Amats\" (שלמה חזק אמץ, Solomon \"for strength and courage\") was a paytan and author of a beloved piyyut for Sukkot, \"El Ram Ḥasin Yah\" (G!D on High, Mighty Yah) on which he added his signature as an acrostic. Unfortunately, little else is known of him. As the piyyut was popular in Afghanistan and is thematically concerned with the archetpal Ushpizin of kabbalistic lore and mystical sukkot custom, we may cautiously assume that Shlomo was a paytan in Afghanistan in the 17th or 18th century, after which the piyyut spread to other communities.",
            "website": "",
            "avatar": "https://opensiddur.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/Keith-Evans-Green-Tree-Yellow-Field-CC-BY-SA-250x250.jpg",
            "profile_link": "https://opensiddur.org/profile/shlomo-hazaq-amats"
        }
    ],
    "date": "2018-09-25",
    "last_updated": "2025-04-04",
    "excerpt": "This is one of my favourite Sukkot piyyutim, not least because of the wonderful and easily singable call-and-response melody! The seven verses each highlight one of the seven traditional ushpizin [mythic guests], and a few years ago I wrote an additional seven verses for the seven female ushpizata <a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/essays/art/ushpizin-and-ushpizata-inviting-the-avot-and-imahot-into-your-sukkah/\">according to the order of Rabbi David Seidenberg (neohasid.org)</a>.  . . .",
    "content": "\n<table style=\"margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" class=\"draggable toggleable-table\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th id=\"x\" style=\"text-align: right;\">Source (Hebrew)</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: left;\">Translation (English)</th>\n<th style=\"text-align: right;\">Amendation (Hebrew)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nאֵל רָם חֲסִין יָהּ<br />\nשׁוֹכֵן עֲלִיָּה<br />\nמַהֵרָה גוֹאֵל<br />\nלְעַם שִׁבְטֵי יָהּ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nG!d on high, mighty Yah,<br />\nWho dwells above<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_1');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[1]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Psalms 89:9&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_1', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nQuickly redeem<br />\nYour people, the tribes of Yah<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_2');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_2');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[2]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_2\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Psalms 122:4&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_2', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nאֵל נִשָּׂא וָרָם<br />\nגַּלֵּה קֵץ נֶעְלָם<br />\nלִבְנֵי אַבְרָהָם<br />\nעַם בָּחַר לוֹ יָהּ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nExalted G!d on high,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_3');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_3');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[3]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_3\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Isaiah 6:1&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_3', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nReveal the hidden end<br />\nTo the children of Avraham,<br />\nThe people chosen by Yah<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_4');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_4');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[4]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_4\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Psalms 135:4&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_4', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nTo the seekers of unity,<br />\nGive loyalty<br />\nAs there was for Ruth<br />\nThe Moabite<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_5');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_5');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[5]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_5\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Ruth 1:18, Ruth 2:2&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_5').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_5', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nלְדוֹרְשֵׁי אַחְדוּת<br />\nתֵּן נֶאֱמָנוּת<br />\nכְּהָיְתָה לְרוּת<br />\nהַמּוֹאֲבִיָּה<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<span class=\"acrostic\">שׁ</span>וֹכֵן בַּשַּׁחַק<br />\nמֵהֶם אַל תִּרְחַק<br />\nלְזֶרַע יִצְחָק<br />\nהוֹצֵא לִרְוָיָה<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nThe One who dwells in cloud,<br />\nDo not distance from them<br />\nThe seed of Yitsḥak,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_6');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_6');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[6]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_6\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Mekhilta de Rebbe Shimon bar Yokhai, ch. 15: &#8220;אבל אנו עמך ונחלתך וצאן מרעיתך בני אברהם אוהבך זרע יצחק יחידך משפחת יעקב בכורך&#8221;&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_6').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_6', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nBrought out into abundance<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_7');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_7');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[7]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_7\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Psalms 66:12&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_7').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_7', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nListen to her voice,<br />\nThe mother, the mistress<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_8');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_8');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_8\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[8]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_8\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Genesis 16:9&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_8').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_8', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnd she laughed, Sarah<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_9');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_9');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_9\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[9]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_9\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Genesis 18:12&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_9').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_9', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nWho was remembered by Yah<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_10');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_10');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_10\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[10]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_10\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Genesis 21:1&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_10').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_10', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nשְׁמַע בְּקֹלָהּ<br />\nהָאֵם הַגְּבִירָה<br />\nוַתִּצְחַק שָׂרָה<br />\nאֵַשֶׁר פָּקָד יָהּ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<span class=\"acrostic\">לְ</span>עִיר תִּפְאַרְתָּךְ<br />\nקְַבֵּץ עֲדָתָךְ<br />\nלִבְנֵי יַעֲקֹב<br />\nשְׁלַח אֵלִיָּה<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nTo the city of your glory<br />\nGather your nation<br />\nTo the children of Ya&#8217;akov<br />\nSend Eliyah<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_11');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_11');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_11\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[11]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_11\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Malakhi 3:23&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_11').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_11', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nAnswer your people<br />\nWhen we cry out to You<br />\nRivka did so,<br />\nShe went out to seek Yah<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_12');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_12');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_12\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[12]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_12\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Genesis 25:22&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_12').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_12', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nתַּשִׁיב לְעַמָּךְ<br />\nבְּקָרְאֵנוּ לָךְ<br />\nכֵּן עָשְׂתָה רִבְקָה<br />\nהִיא דּוֹרֶשֶׁת יָהּ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<span class=\"acrostic\">מִ</span>קְדַּשׁ הֲדוֹמָךְ<br />\nיְָשִׁיר בּוֹ עַמָּךְ<br />\nבְּשִׁירַת מֹשֶׁה<br />\nנָבִיא בְּחִיר יָהּ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nIn your holy Resting-place<br />\nYour people will sing<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_13');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_13');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_13\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[13]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_13\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Isaiah 66:1, 1 Chronicles 28:2&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_13').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_13', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nThe song of Moshe<br />\nThe prophet chosen by Yah<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_14');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_14');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_14\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[14]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_14\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Shir HaShirim Rabba 1:11&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_14').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_14', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nShe watched the river,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_15');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_15');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_15\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[15]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_15\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Exodus 2:4&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_15').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_15', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nShe saw the sea split<br />\nWe will sing with her<br />\nMiryam the prophet of Yah<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_16');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_16');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_16\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[16]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_16\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Exodus 15:20&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_16').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_16', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nמֵי נָהָר שָׁמְרָה<br />\nקְרִיאָת סוּף רָאָתָה<br />\nעִמָּהּ נָשִׁירָה<br />\nמִרְיָם נְּבִיאָת יָהּ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<span class=\"acrostic\">הָ</span>רֵם עַם אֶבְיוֹן<br />\nוּבְנֵה אַפִּרְיוֹן<br />\nלְגֶזַע אַהֲרֹן<br />\nיַקְרִיבוּ לְיָהּ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nRaise up an impoverished people,<br />\nAnd build a canopy<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_17');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_17');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_17\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[17]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_17\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Song of Songs 3:9, Shir HaShirim Rabba 3:1&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_17').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_17', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nFor the family of Aharon,<br />\nWho will sacrifice to Yah\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nFor our enemies, remember<br />\nYou will deliver them to a woman<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_18');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_18');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_18\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[18]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_18\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Judges 4:9&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_18').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_18', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nDevorah, burning<br />\nLike a fiery torch of Yah<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_19');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_19');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_19\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[19]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_19\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Judges 4:4&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_19').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_19', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nלְאוֹיבֵנוּ זְכֹר<br />\nבְּיַד אִשָּׁה תִּמְכֹּר<br />\nדְּבוֹרָה בּוֹעֶרֶת<br />\nכְּלַפִּידָת יָהּ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<span class=\"acrostic\">חַזֵּק</span> וְאַסֵּף<br />\nלְבֵית יוֹסֵף<br />\nיִרְבּוּ וְיִפְרוּ<br />\nכְּגֶפֶן פּוֹרִיָה<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nStrengthen and increase<br />\nThe house of Yosef<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_20');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_20');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_20\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[20]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_20\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Zechariah 10:6&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_20').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_20', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nLet them multiply<br />\nLike a fruitful vine<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_21');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_21');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_21\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[21]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_21\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Cf. Psalms 128:3&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_21').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_21', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nGive strength in Your glory<br />\nSo that we can say in justice<br />\nThat she was right, Tamar,<span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_22');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_22');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_22\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[22]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_22\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Genesis 38:26&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_22').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_22', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nThe mother of the anointed of Yah <span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_23');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_23');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_23\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[23]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_23\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Genesis 38:29-30; Ruth 4:18-22&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_23').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_23', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script>\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nעֻזָּה בֶּהָדָר<br />\nבְּצֶדֶק נֹאמַר<br />\nכִּי צָדְקָה תָּמָר<br />\nאֵם מְשִׁיחַ יָהּ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<span class=\"acrostic\">אַמֵּץ</span> בֶּן דָּוִד<br />\nוְיִשְׁפֹּט תָּמִיד<br />\nכָּל צַר תַּשְׁמִיד<br />\nגָּרֵשׁ מֵעִיר יָהּ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nGive courage to the son of David<br />\nThat he might eternally judge<br />\nDestroy all trouble<br />\nBanish it from the city of Yah\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\n<p></span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"36%\">\n<div class=\"english\" lang=\"eng-Latn\">\nGrant peace to Your walls<br />\nRedeem Your city<br />\nAccording to the tears of Raḥel <span class=\"footnote_referrer\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_24');\" onkeypress=\"footnote_moveToReference__1('footnote_plugin_reference__1_24');\" ><sup id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_24\" class=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text\">[24]</sup></a><span id=\"footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_24\" class=\"footnote_tooltip\"> Jeremiah 31:15&nbsp;</span></span><script type=\"text/javascript\"> jQuery('#footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_24').tooltip({ tip: '#footnote_plugin_tooltip_text__1_24', tipClass: 'footnote_tooltip', effect: 'fade', predelay: 0, fadeInSpeed: 200, delay: 400, fadeOutSpeed: 200, position: 'center right', relative: true, offset: [0, 0], });</script><br />\nAnd the Shekhina of Yah\n</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top;\" width=\"26%\">\n<div class=\"liturgy\" lang=\"heb-Hebr\">\nתֵּן שָׁלוֹם בְּחֵיל<br />\nלְעִירָךְ גּוֹאֵל<br />\nעַל דִּמְעָת רָחֵל<br />\nוּשְׁכִינַת יָהּ<br />\n</span></div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<hr />\n<p>This is one of my favourite Sukkot piyyutim, not least because of the wonderful and easily singable call-and-response melody! The seven verses each highlight one of the seven traditional ushpizin [mythic guests], and a few years ago [in 2012] I wrote an additional seven verses for the seven female ushpizata <a href=\"https://opensiddur.org/essays/art/ushpizin-and-ushpizata-inviting-the-avot-and-imahot-into-your-sukkah/\">according to the order of Rabbi David Seidenberg (neohasid.org)</a>.</p>\n<p>The original lyrics for El Ram Ḥasin Yah, and a recording of the traditional melody, can be found at the <a href=\"http://web.nli.org.il/sites/nlis/he/song/Pages/Song.aspx?SongID=919#5,51,3251,905\">Piyut archive</a> hosted by the National Library of Israel.</p>\n<div class=\"speaker-mute footnotes_reference_container\"> <div class=\"footnote_container_prepare\"><p><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_label pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\">Notes</span><span role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_reference_container_collapse_button\" style=\"display: none;; display: none;\" onclick=\"footnote_expand_collapse_reference_container__1();\"></span></p></div> <div id=\"footnote_references_container__1\" style=\"\"><table class=\"footnotes_table footnote-reference-container\"><caption class=\"accessibility\">Notes</caption> <tbody> \r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_1\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_1');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >1</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Cf. Psalms 89:9</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_2\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_2');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >2</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Cf. Psalms 122:4</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_3\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_3');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >3</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Cf. Isaiah 6:1</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_4\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"footnote_moveToAnchor__1('footnote_plugin_tooltip__1_4');\"><a role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" class=\"footnote_plugin_link\" >4</a></th> <td class=\"footnote_plugin_text\">Cf. Psalms 135:4</td></tr>\r\n\r\n<tr class=\"footnotes_plugin_reference_row\"> <th scope=\"row\" id=\"footnote_plugin_reference__1_5\" class=\"footnote_plugin_index pointer\" onclick=\"foot